robot.logic
Class TargetLogic

java.lang.Object
  robot.logic.TargetLogic

public abstract class TargetLogic
extends Object

TargetLogic calls RobotShoot and RobotDrive and asks for data from RobotCamera to direct targeting; update() must be called periodically. This class doesn't directly interface with any motors.

Author:
Nathan
